Methodology :
Implement the EM algorithm to generate alignments of English phenome sequences to Japanese phenome sequences


Input: 

training-data
Set of word pairs of English phenome sequence and Japanese phenome sequence

NO_ITERATIONS
The number of iterations to run EM for.


Output: 

alignments - Set of all possible alignments for each word pair
epron-jpron.alignment - Correct alignment file generated using the EM algorithm
epron-jpron-unsupervised.wfst - A WFST containing weighted transitions of English phenome sequences to Japanese phenome sequences



To run the program use the following command:

python generate-alignments.py training-data alignments 
python EM-epron-jpron.py alignments NO_ITERATIONS epron-jpron.alignment epron-jpron-unsupervised.wfst

